15:42.367 --> 15:44.266
love to complain about.

15:44.266 --> 15:45.900
- We have seen Republicans

15:45.900 --> 15:48.500
rig the system
with their gerrymandering,

15:48.500 --> 15:50.600
often illegal gerrymandering.

15:50.600 --> 15:53.400
- There is gerrymandering
to a fare-thee-well in states

15:53.400 --> 15:55.333
controlled
